==English==

===Etymology===
From [[Mala]] or [[Malai]], the word for mountain and [[alam]], the word for place in the same language.

===Proper noun===
'''Malayalam'''

# [[Dravidian]] language spoken in the state of [[Kerala]], [[India]]

